{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"562cf2d340","title":"对第四次全国公安会议决议草案的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"44854175f6","index":0,"year":1951,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"562cf2d340"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"e7d3135f13","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本文第一、二、三部分是毛泽东的批语，第四至第七部分，用宋体字排印的是毛泽东加写的文字。"},{"id":"406f546302","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"瑞卿，即罗瑞卿，当时任中央人民政府公安部部长。"},{"id":"b0e5dbba55","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、政务院政治法律委员会副主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"50f4a88567","type":"title","text":"对第四次全国公安会议决议草案的批语和修改”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"e7d3135f13","type":"paragraph","text":"瑞卿同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"406f546302","type":"paragraph","text":"已阅，略有修改，可以此稿发给到会人，征求意见，于星期六日来中央讨论一次。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"b0e5dbba55","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"63391fcecb","type":"paragraph","text":"九月六日上午三时瑞卿、彭真同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"0b083fc220","type":"paragraph","text":"已加修改，请你【们】再加的，印发到会同志及政治局客同志。侯会议提出新的意见，再作一次修改，就可定案。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"67596e38bc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"90109a82c8","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十一日","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"42b714eef8","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"621a4ca3a4","type":"paragraph","text":"瑞卿同志：","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"e37c008861","type":"paragraph","text":"已看过，略有修改。印刷时注意校对勿错","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"c6817a710d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"15a952ba65","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十五日","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"35bd2714cc","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"d3c935f02b","type":"paragraph","text":"整个镇压反革命的工作，必须在各级党委的统一领导之下。一切公安机关和有关镇压反革命的机关的负责同志，都必须和过去一样，坚决接受党委的领导","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"051f22f7db","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"f20b890c7b","type":"paragraph","text":"鉴于过去有些县区乡，因为党政组织不纯，在镇压反革命运动中发生了镇压不彻底的现象，或乱捕乱杀的错误，因此决定：一切由于基层党政机关内部不纯以致反革命镇压不彻底的地区，或是犯了大错误的地区（这种地区在全国说来是少数），在县区乡党政组织没有整顿好和领导力量没有加强以前，除现行犯外，必须一律继续停止捕人杀人，等待县区乡组织整顿好了（包括在县区乡组织中清出可能有的反革命分子在内）和领导力量加强了之后，再去进行镇压反革命的工作。对于此种地区，必须忍耐，不可性急","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"447bde522c","type":"subtitle","text":"六","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"cab344cfb2","type":"paragraph","text":"在镇压反革命确实已经达到了彻底程度的县、区、乡及某些市区，即应结束镇压反革命的运动，转入经常的对暗藏反革命分子作斗争的工作。此类县区乡或市区的判定，由省（区）市级公安机关负责（经党委讨论通过），报告大行政区及中央公安部备案","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"1b594f6b63","type":"subtitle","text":"七","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"},{"id":"6b2f5b9e7e","type":"paragraph","text":"加强对领袖、对首长、对首脑机关及重要民主人士的警卫和保卫工作，同反革命的暗害活动作尖锐的斗争，经常保持充分的警慢性，必须引起十分注意。责成专署以上和师以上各级公安机关和保卫机关负责，收集各地反革命分子的暗害案件（包括已破案和未破案的）归于一类，加以清理，找出线索，研究处理办法，做出结论，报告中央公安部。","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340"}],"page":{"id":"fbd473839a","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"562cf2d340","start":485,"end":487}}}},"__N_SSG":true}